Class EventGraphProjection<Event>

public class EventGraphProjection<Event> extends Object implements Projection<Event,​EventGraph<Event>>
The identity projection from event graphs to event graphs.

This projection can be used as an alternative to constructing event graphs via the static factory methods defined on EventGraph. If some function is parametrized over any Projection, this projection can be provided to obtain a pure syntax tree representation of the effect it would compute.

If one wishes to specifically construct an EventGraph, prefer the static factory methods on that class.

See Also:
EventGraph, Projection
